Package album

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Album
    This class defines the abstract data type that models an album in a collection of albums
    Collection
    This class defines the array list data structure to hold the album collection and provide the operations to manage the collection
    CollectionManager
    This is a class handles the I/O for the user
    Date
    This class defines the Date abstract data type with year, month, and day
    RunProject1
    This is a driver class to test run Project 1
